@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home - Blazor Tailwind Project</PageTitle>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 selection:bg-indigo-500/30">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 pb-24 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-40">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(45rem_50rem_at_top,theme(colors.indigo.900/0.3),theme(colors.gray.900))]"></div>
        
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-indigo-400 ring-1 ring-inset ring-indigo-500/20">
                        v1.0.0 Alpha
                    </span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="focus:outline-none text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-gray-400">
                    Blazor Tailwind Project
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-400">
                    Uma aplicação moderna construída com o poder do <strong>Blazor .NET 10</strong> e a flexibilidade do <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong>. Explore a integração perfeita de componentes interativos e design utilitário.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
                    <a href="/Account/Register" class="rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600 transition-all">
                        Começar Agora
                    </a>
                    <a href="#about" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white group">
                        Saiba mais <span aria-hidden="true" class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24">
        
        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about" class="py-24 sm:py-32">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
                <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Sobre o Projeto</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
                    Performance C# com Estilo Moderno
                </p>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-400 text-justify">
                    Este projeto foi desenvolvido como um laboratório de estudos do <strong>Blazor Web App</strong> no .NET 10. 
                    O foco principal é a integração nativa com o <strong>Tailwind CSS 4</strong>, perrmitindo um controle total sobre a interface.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
                <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0010 1zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 10-6 0V9h6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                            ASP.NET Core Identity
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-400">
                            <p class="flex-auto text-justify">Sistema completo de autenticação e autorização configurado, incluindo registro de usuários e suporte a Passkeys.</p>
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path d="M11 2.25V1h1.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5H11zM11 5V3.75h1.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5H11zM7.5 1h1.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5H7.5V1zM7.5 3.75h1.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5H7.5V3.75z" />
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 1A1.5 1.5 0 003 2.5V3h4v-.5A1.5 1.5 0 005.5 1h-1zM13 3h4v-.5A1.5 1.5 0 0015.5 1h-1A1.5 1.5 0 0013 2.5V3zM3 4v13.5A1.5 1.5 0 004.5 19h11a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V4H3zm4.735 4.32a.75.75 0 00-1.47-.28l-1 5.25a.75.75 0 101.47.28l1-5.25zm5 0a.75.75 0 00-1.47-.28l-1 5.25a.75.75 0 101.47.28l1-5.25z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                            Entity Framework Core
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-400">
                            <p class="flex-auto text-justify">Persistência de dados utilizando SQL Server e o padrão Repository para gerenciamento de naves espaciais (Starships).</p>
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M15.312 11.424a5.5 5.5 0 01-9.201 2.466l-.312-.311h2.433a.75.75 0 000-1.5H3.989a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v4.242a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-2.43l.31.31a7 7 0 0011.712-3.138.75.75 0 00-1.449-.39zm1.23-6.242a.75.75 0 00-1.5 0v2.43l-.31-.31A7 7 0 003.02 10.44a.75.75 0 001.449.39 5.5 5.5 0 019.201-2.466l.312.311h-2.433a.75.75 0 000 1.5h4.243a.75.75 0 00.75-.75V5.182z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                            Modern Dev Workflow
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-400">
                            <p class="flex-auto text-justify">Hot Reload, processamento JIT do Tailwind CSS e uma estrutura de componentes reutilizáveis.</p>
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Starship CTA -->
        <section class="mt-32 relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-indigo-500/10 px-6 py-24 shadow-2xl rounded-3xl sm:px-24 xl:py-32">
            <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Gerencie sua Frota Estelar</h2>
            <p class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-xl text-center text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
                Acesse o módulo CRUD para listar, criar e editar naves espaciais utilizando componentes Blazor altamente responsivos.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
                <a href="/Starship/List" class="rounded-md bg-white px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white transition-all">
                    Acessar Frota
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-900 border-t border-white/10 mt-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-12 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6 md:order-2">
                <p class="text-xs leading-5 text-gray-400">Blazor + Tailwind CSS © 2026</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 md:order-1 md:mt-0">
                <p class="text-center text-xs leading-5 text-gray-400">
                    Construído com .NET.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
